  "text": "COCs were homogenized in IPA buffer and centrifuged as described above. The soluble fraction was incubated with 20 l of anti-PDE3A [CITATION_1] preadsorbed on Protein A-Sepharose (Sigma). The homogenate was immunoprecipitated overnight at 4ЊC by gentle agitation. A negative control was performed by using comparable amounts of preimmune serum. At the end of incubation, samples were centrifuged at 1000 ϫ g for 5 min. The pellets were washed three times with PBS and 0.1% BSA. After washing, the pellets were resuspended in Tris-BSA (40 mM Tris-HCl pH 8.0, 1 mg/ ml BSA) before measuring PDE activity.",
